entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have successfully rescued the fifth Imperial Officer from the Rebel Detainment Facility.
entries.journal_entry_description: Search the Rebel Detainment Facility for the next Imperial Officer being held prisoner.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Defeat Froud in combat and take his SpecForce Armor.
entries.task01_journal_entry_title: Get the disguise from Titus Froud
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Defeat Rebel SpecForce Troopers located North of the prisoner control room near the power generators.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Defeat some Roaming Sentry Droids patrolling the hallways.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Search the holding cells located at the Northeast rear holding wing of the facility.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Give the officer the disguise you have.
